[17/06/2017 20:42:35] <font color="#ffff00">Oh.</font>
[17/06/2017 20:42:37] <font color="#ffff00">(SUSPIRA)</font>
[17/06/2017 20:42:40] <font color="#ffff00">Oh, qué maravilla.</font>
[17/06/2017 20:42:42] <font color="#ffffff">¿Le gusta?</font>
